---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '@/components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Flow Agents — Agent-facing vertical of Kontour Flow · Kontour AI"
  description="Keep your coding agent on the required path across Claude Code, Codex, Kiro, and GitHub Actions."
>
  <Nav active="flow-agents" />

  <section class="contour-bg" style="
    padding: 10rem var(--spacing-page) 6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-edge);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  ">
    <div style="
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 10%;
      width: 680px;
      height: 460px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(225,221,211,0.045) 0%, transparent 68%);
      pointer-events: none;
    "></div>

    <div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <div style="
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 5rem;
        align-items: center;
      ">
        <div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <span class="trust-badge trust-badge--proposed">coming soon</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-chalk-3);">github.com/kontourai/flow-agents</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="animate-fade-up" style="
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: var(--color-chalk);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
          ">Flow Agents</h1>

          <p class="animate-fade-up delay-100" style="
            font-family: var(--font-mono);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--color-chalk-2);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
          ">the agent-facing vertical of Kontour Flow</p>

          <p class="animate-fade-up delay-200" style="
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--color-chalk-2);
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 540px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
          ">
            Agents are useful out of the box. They get fragile when work is
            long, parallel, risky, or knowledge-heavy. Flow Agents wraps Claude
            Code, Codex, Kiro, and GitHub Actions with the just-in-time
            guidance, workflow state, and evidence gates that survive long
            sessions and context compaction. You ask for the outcome you want.
            The system supplies the right instructions, tools, memory, and
            checks underneath.
          </p>

          <div class="animate-fade-up delay-300" style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="https://github.com/kontourai/flow-agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary" data-umami-event="flow-agents-hero-github">
              View on GitHub →
            </a>
            <a href="/flow" class="btn-ghost" data-umami-event="flow-agents-hero-flow">
              Explore Flow
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-fade-in delay-300">
          <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
            <div style="
              position: absolute;
              top: 0;
              left: 0;
              right: 0;
              height: 2px;
              background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-chalk-2), transparent);
            "></div>
            <div class="label-sm" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-chalk-2);">Status</div>
            <p style="color: var(--color-chalk-2); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0;">
              Flow Agents is the agent-facing distribution layer for Kontour
              Flow and Veritas evidence. It's actively being built; first
              public release is upcoming.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer active="flow-agents" />
</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    section > div > div[style*="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr"] {
      display: flex !important;
      flex-direction: column !important;
    }
  }
</style>
